headline: Nasdaq (NDAQ): Assessing Fair Value After a Year of Quiet but Strong Gains
summary: Nasdaq (NDAQ) has grabbed investor attention this week, though there isn’t a single headline-making event driving the stock’s movement. Sometimes these quieter periods can be just as thought-provoking as major announcements, since shifts in price without obvious news can lead investors to question whether the market is signaling something deeper, such as a change in how the company is being valued or broader shifts in sentiment about where it is headed next.
